full_text: Screened by NARA, 7/31/2023 OMB #1115-0064 Expires 3/31/84 U. S. Department of Justice Immigration and Naturalization Service Notice of Preliminary Naturalization Hearing Naturalization and Citizenship Branch 300 NORTH LCS ANGELES STREET File or A # 21 526 240 Date 5/07/1984 LOS ANGELES, CA 90012 You are hereby notified to appear for a hearing on your (your child's) application for naturalization at the DATE, TIME, AND PLACE, shown below. Date 6/04/1984 Time 900 AM GOVINDRAM TOTARAM LATHI 5627 LEXINGTON AVE. APT. 6 HOLLYWOOD, CA 90038 Place 300 NORTH LOS ANGELES STREET harrrott stell LOS ANGELES, CA 90012 FEDERAL BUILDING - DOWNTOWN ROOM NUMBER- 8010 You MUST BRING the following with you: - This letter, with the Personal Description Form on the REVERSE SIDE COMPLETELY FILLED IN. Alien Registration Receipt Card. MICHAEL H. LANDON, JR. Any evidence of Selective Service Registration. Any documents you have which you used in connection with any entries into the United States. DISTRICT DIRECTOR Those items noted on the reverse side of this letter which are applicable to you. Filing Fee. $50 NCNEY ORDER CR CASH (NO COINS). Please KEEP this APPOINTMENT even if you do not have all the items noted above or those on the back. However, you MUST bring the Filling Fee. Form N 430A IMPORTANT - PLEASE SEE REVERSE
